1. *Sanjam* da putujem po celom svetu. (I dream of traveling all over the world.)
2. Često *sanjam* o tome kako bi bilo lepo da imam svoju kuću. (I often dream about how nice it would be to have my own house.)
3. *Sanjao sam* da letim iznad oblaka. (I dreamt that I was flying above the clouds.)
4. Ona *sanja* da će postati glumica jednog dana. (She dreams of becoming an actress one day.)
5. *Sanjali su* da su pobedili na takmičenju. (They dreamed that they had won the competition.)
6. Čim zatvorim oči, *sanjam* o tebi. (As soon as I close my eyes, I dream about you.)
7. *Sanjala sam* da sam zaglavila na pustom ostrvu. (I dreamt that I was stranded on a deserted island.)
8. Nikada ne bih mogla ni da *sanjam* da vozim takmičarski automobil. (I could never even dream of driving a race car.)
9. Deca *sanjaju* o tome da postanu superheroji. (Children dream of becoming superheroes.)
10. *Sanjao sam* da se nalazim na vrhu planine. (I dreamt that I was on top of a mountain.)